snippet: Harry Kane's superb scoring streak continued as Tottenham Hotspur survived some late nerves to beat Everton 3-2 at White Hart Lane on Sunday and cut Chelsea's lead at the top of the Premier League to seven points....

headline.main: Liver Transplant Surgical Pioneer Dr. Thomas Starzl Dies
headline.print_headline: Liver Transplant Surgical Pioneer Dr. Thomas Starzl Dies

lead_paragraph: Harry Kane's superb scoring streak continued as Tottenham Hotspur survived some late nerves to beat Everton 3-2 at White Hart Lane on Sunday and cut Chelsea's lead at the top of the Premier League to seven points.
